            <div class="grid1">
                <div class="column">
                    <p>Easyjet Airlines is a low-cost airline group in England headquartered at London. The airline serves domestic and international scheduled services on over 1,000 routes in more than 30 countries via its affiliate airlines EasyJet UK, EasyJet Switzerland, and EasyJet Europe with a fleet of 310 aircraft. Easyjet is known for its cabin and onboard services, loyalty products, and business travels. </p>
                </div>
