            </div>
            <p>If you have plans to book flight tickets from Easyjet Airlines, make sure you check the ongoing offers and deals, flight booking, and cancellation policy. For your ease, below is an overview of Easyjet Airlines’ cancelation policy. </p>
            <h2>Cancellation policy </h2>
            <p>According to <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/easyjet-airlines-cancellation-policy.aspx">Easyjet Airlines’ cancellation policy</a>, you can cancel a flight ticket within 24 hours of booking without paying any cancellation fee. The airline is not bound to return any refund if you cross the time limitation of 24 hours. But you can still make changes to the flight. </p>
            <p>If you couldn’t board the flight due to some unavoidable reasons, the airline may offer you a gift voucher that may hold the same value as the price of the fare that you can use within six months. The airline may also ask to submit relevant documents as the reason for <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/cancellation-policy.aspx">flight cancellation</a>. </p>
            <h3>Refund policy </h3>
            <p>
                You can <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">cancel a flight</a> ticket within 24 hours of booking without paying any cancellation fee if you completed the purchase 7 days or more before the initially scheduled departure flight. You will receive the refund after the deduction of the cancellation fee based on fare category, method of purchase, mode of payment, departure date, departure, arrival city, and flight types. <br>
                Moreover, the airline may not issue a refund if you or the co-passenger faces any health issues, death of the passenger, or influence of the Military or Government.
            </p>
            <h2>FAQs</h2>
            <h3>How to cancel a flight ticket with Easyjet Airlines? </h3>
            <p>You can call the Easyjet Airlines customer care office and inform them about the cancellation. Also, you can visit the official website of the airlines and cancel your flight ticket. </p>
            <h3>How can I make the request for a refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>You can visit the official website of Easyjet Airlines and make a request for a refund or you can call customer care. It takes time to process the refunds; hence, you may receive refunds within 7 to 20 business days. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>There can be a possibility that your replacement flight delays your arrival by 2 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get compensation. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>You can check if your flight is refundable by visiting the official website of the airline and entering the ticket or document number and the Easyjet Airlines website will display refund eligibility and information. </p>
